This pure Python 3.5+ package contains helpful reference file organizational tools and data visulaization functions that may be useful in analyzing observations from the Single Object Slitless Spectroscopy (SOSS) mode of the Near-Infrared Imager and Slitless Spectrograph (NIRISS) instrument onboard the James Webb Space Telescope (JWST).


